Bill ... For spare batteries, take a look at B.G.Micro's BAT1024.
They are two AA cells in series, 800mAh ... 10 batteries (20 cells)
for US$5.95.  I've made several spare HandyBoard battery packs using
these cells ... and they all work great.
    http://www.bgmicro.com/

